cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CY 

This paper is about sentiment analysis in Twitter, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with the intersection of computer science and linguistics. The task also involves analyzing large amounts of data, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, machine learning algorithms are used, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.CY (Computational Geometry).
